SQTagUtil
public static enum SQTagUtil.SQBase
extends java.lang.Enum<SQTagUtil.SQBase>

The ordinals of these are stored in the high-order 2 bits of each byte of the SQ tag. Note that these have the convenient property that the binary complement of each ordinal, masked to the two low-order bits, is the complementary base.
